author: lundblad
msg: Support a new format in the entries file that is not XML based and that
includes the format number of this working copy.
* TODO: Remove done entry; add another.
(read_entries): Read entries in the new format.
(write_str, write_bool, write_revnum, write_time, write_val): New functions.
(write_entry): Change output argument to pointer to stringbuf.  Write entries
(svn_wc__entries_write): Write entries file in new format.
(svn_wc__entries_init): Move further down in the file.  Use new entries
(check_adm_exists): Try to read format number from entries file and fall back
on format if that doesn't work.
(init_adm): Update comments to indicate why we create .svn/format.
(do_open): Read format from entries, falling back to format if necessary.
(svn_wc_check_wc): Read format number from entries, falling back on format
